            "sub_heading": "",
            "heading": "#4. Fold inside the folds",
            "text": "<p>If your saree has elaborate embroidery or zardozi work, or sequin work or mirror work, you can get a netted lining attaches to preserve the thread work and keeping it from getting tangled. Also be sure to fold this inside the folds of the saree in order to preserve its sheen.<\/p>",
