            "text_size": "40,15",
            "txt_align": "start",
            "sub_heading": "",
            "heading": "#5. The perfect storing method",
            "text": "<p>1. Use naphthalene balls to keep the moths and silverfish away, don’t keep them in direct contact with your saree as they tend to discolour any zari work.<br\/><br\/>2. An even better option is to use dry neem leaves as they have anti-pest and anti-fungal properties. Use neem leaves if you can.<br\/><br\/>3. Storing the silk sarees in a cool dark place will keep your saree from fading or discolouring.<\/p>",
            "subhd_color": "#222222",
            "hd_color": "#222222",
            "des_color": "#878787",
